<font color="yellow">Dad. Is that what you told Seong Joon?</font>

634
00:39:34,844 --> 00:39:36,914
<font color="yellow">Do you think he didn't know?</font>

635
00:39:37,444 --> 00:39:39,774
<font color="yellow">It all comes down to a decision in the end.</font>

636
00:39:40,344 --> 00:39:42,084
<font color="yellow">He can either be my son-in-law and bear the disgrace,</font>

637
00:39:42,844 --> 00:39:44,914
<font color="yellow">or he can keep his petty pride...</font>

638
00:39:44,974 --> 00:39:46,544
<font color="yellow">and stay in the lower class.</font>

639
00:39:46,644 --> 00:39:47,814
<font color="yellow">Dad!</font>

640
00:39:48,844 --> 00:39:52,514
<font color="yellow">If that was your plan, why didn't you just let me run the company?</font>

641
00:39:53,214 --> 00:39:55,944
<font color="yellow">Grandma is a woman, but she ran the company by herself.</font>

642
00:39:56,314 --> 00:39:58,274
<font color="yellow">Don't talk about your grandmother.</font>

643
00:39:58,614 --> 00:40:01,014
<font color="yellow">She's too weak and compassionate.</font>

644
00:40:01,214 --> 00:40:03,474
<font color="yellow">If it wasn't for me, our company...</font>

645
00:40:03,914 --> 00:40:06,044
<font color="yellow">would've been broken apart long ago.</font>

646
00:40:06,114 --> 00:40:09,514
<font color="yellow">Your own daughter is about to be broken apart.</font>

647
00:40:10,544 --> 00:40:12,114
<font color="yellow">If you keep doing this,</font>

648
00:40:13,014 --> 00:40:14,414
<font color="yellow">I'll kill myself.</font>

649
00:40:15,474 --> 00:40:16,544
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

650
00:40:19,044 --> 00:40:20,174
<font color="yellow">(Letter of Resignation)</font>

651
00:40:37,614 --> 00:40:41,544
<font color="yellow">(Letter of Resignation)</font>

652
00:40:57,644 --> 00:41:00,544
<font color="yellow">The more I think about it, the more I get upset.</font>

653
00:41:01,514 --> 00:41:03,414
<font color="yellow">What are you going to do?</font>

654
00:41:03,544 --> 00:41:06,274
<font color="yellow">He's your son. It's not like you can kill him or anything.</font>

655
00:41:07,114 --> 00:41:08,644
<font color="yellow">Mother. Hyung Seop says...</font>

656
00:41:08,914 --> 00:41:11,214
<font color="yellow">he can understand Seong Sik.</font>

657
00:41:11,374 --> 00:41:14,474
<font color="yellow">He says Seong Sik is a poor kid who gave up things for his brothers.</font>

658
00:41:14,674 --> 00:41:15,844
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

659
00:41:16,014 --> 00:41:18,514
<font color="yellow">Look. There is no one in this world...</font>

660
00:41:18,514 --> 00:41:20,914
<font color="yellow">whom Hyung Seop can't understand.</font>

661
00:41:21,014 --> 00:41:24,514
<font color="yellow">He should be scolding and yelling at Seong Sik.</font>

662
00:41:24,544 --> 00:41:25,914
<font color="yellow">How could he say he understands?</font>

663
00:41:26,714 --> 00:41:28,214
<font color="yellow">I just can't believe it.</font>

664
00:41:29,114 --> 00:41:31,644
<font color="yellow">As a father, he should be stricter.</font>

665
00:41:31,644 --> 00:41:33,514
<font color="yellow">He's just too soft.</font>

666
00:41:33,744 --> 00:41:35,274
<font color="yellow">When he gets older,</font>

667
00:41:35,274 --> 00:41:37,814
<font color="yellow">our children will all look down on him.</font>

668
00:41:38,314 --> 00:41:40,344
<font color="yellow">Don't worry. You have Seong Joon.</font>

669
00:41:40,344 --> 00:41:44,114
<font color="yellow">He will believe anything Hyung Seop says.</font>

670
00:41:44,114 --> 00:41:47,814
<font color="yellow">You only need one child who understands how you feel.</font>

671
00:41:48,014 --> 00:41:50,214
<font color="yellow">Don't expect all of them to understand you.</font>

672
00:41:50,874 --> 00:41:52,144
<font color="yellow">By the way,</font>

673
00:41:52,674 --> 00:41:54,944
<font color="yellow">what are we going to do with Seong Joon?</font>

674
00:41:54,974 --> 00:41:56,044
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

675
00:41:56,114 --> 00:41:59,084
<font color="yellow">What if he marries that girl named Mi Joo?</font>

676
00:41:59,274 --> 00:42:02,444
<font color="yellow">She's the only daughter of the chairman.</font>

677
00:42:02,444 --> 00:42:04,914
<font color="yellow">It should be different from how Seong Hoon...</font>

678
00:42:04,914 --> 00:42:06,914
<font color="yellow">and Seong Sik got married.</font>

679
00:42:06,974 --> 00:42:08,744
<font color="yellow">Goodness. You're right.</font>

680
00:42:09,314 --> 00:42:11,474
<font color="yellow">I guess we shouldn't be too happy that...</font>

681
00:42:11,474 --> 00:42:13,474
<font color="yellow">she's the chairman's beautiful daughter.</font>

682
00:42:13,974 --> 00:42:15,174
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

683
00:42:19,344 --> 00:42:21,744
<font color="yellow">By the way, Mother.</font>

684
00:42:23,774 --> 00:42:25,714
<font color="yellow">When Seong Joon gets married,</font>

685
00:42:26,614 --> 00:42:27,874
<font color="yellow">his mother...</font>

686
00:42:28,374 --> 00:42:30,374
<font color="yellow">- will come, right? - What?</font>

687
00:42:32,144 --> 00:42:34,544
<font color="yellow">I've been holding it in...</font>

688
00:42:35,114 --> 00:42:37,474
<font color="yellow">for more than 20 years,</font>

689
00:42:38,844 --> 00:42:40,814
<font color="yellow">but I'm going to see her face...</font>

690
00:42:41,584 --> 00:42:43,774
<font color="yellow">when Seong Joon gets married.</font>

691
00:42:43,944 --> 00:42:45,314
<font color="yellow">Why would you do that?</font>

692
00:42:45,844 --> 00:42:49,674
<font color="yellow">You've raised him for over 20 years. He's your son, not anybody else's.</font>

693
00:42:50,084 --> 00:42:54,374
<font color="yellow">You're a woman, too. I'm sure you understand how I feel.</font>

694
00:42:54,374 --> 00:42:57,844
<font color="yellow">Of course I do. I understand how you must feel.</font>

695
00:42:58,014 --> 00:43:00,314
<font color="yellow">I don't know if anyone would, but I do understand.</font>

696
00:43:00,614 --> 00:43:03,474
<font color="yellow">You've treated all of your four children alike.</font>

697
00:43:03,844 --> 00:43:07,114
<font color="yellow">I know you must have wanted to hate him and be mean to him,</font>

698
00:43:07,614 --> 00:43:10,614
<font color="yellow">but you have been trying so hard not to.</font>

699
00:43:11,144 --> 00:43:15,084
<font color="yellow">Jeong Ae. That's why I've been always grateful to you.</font>

700
00:43:15,444 --> 00:43:18,744
<font color="yellow">Why would you want to see her face after all this time?</font>

701
00:43:18,944 --> 00:43:20,514
<font color="yellow">Why would you want to dig up the past?</font>

702
00:43:22,174 --> 00:43:23,774
<font color="yellow">I just want to know...</font>

703
00:43:24,214 --> 00:43:25,544
<font color="yellow">what kind of person she is.</font>

704
00:43:26,444 --> 00:43:29,344
<font color="yellow">She abandoned her child,</font>

705
00:43:29,584 --> 00:43:31,214
<font color="yellow">and never contacted us.</font>

706
00:43:31,544 --> 00:43:33,874
<font color="yellow">I know. I want to see her, too.</font>

707
00:43:34,214 --> 00:43:36,944
<font color="yellow">You know Hyung Seop isn't someone who would cheat on his wife,</font>

708
00:43:36,974 --> 00:43:40,014
<font color="yellow">but he cheated on you with that woman.</font>

709
00:43:40,014 --> 00:43:41,544
<font color="yellow">I want to see her, too.</font>

710
00:43:42,274 --> 00:43:45,014
<font color="yellow">But Jeong Ae. You should keep this to yourself.</font>

711
00:43:45,214 --> 00:43:48,574
<font color="yellow">If you dig it up, it will only hurt your feelings.</font>

712
00:43:51,614 --> 00:43:52,844
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

713
00:43:53,574 --> 00:43:56,074
<font color="yellow">Anyway, I'm having...</font>

714
00:43:56,674 --> 00:43:59,514
<font color="yellow">such a hard time because of my kids these days.</font>

715
00:43:59,874 --> 00:44:01,874
<font color="yellow">I know. My goodness.</font>

716
00:44:02,174 --> 00:44:03,914
<font color="yellow">It's never peaceful in our house.</font>

717
00:44:22,244 --> 00:44:23,374
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

718
00:44:26,114 --> 00:44:27,174
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

719
00:44:27,714 --> 00:44:29,144
<font color="yellow">Are you coming home from work?</font>

720
00:44:29,774 --> 00:44:30,874
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

721
00:44:35,044 --> 00:44:36,314
<font color="yellow">You got off work quite late.</font>

722
00:44:36,974 --> 00:44:37,974
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

723
00:44:38,214 --> 00:44:39,844
<font color="yellow">I was busy at work today.</font>

724
00:44:42,144 --> 00:44:43,444
<font color="yellow">What line of work are you in?</font>

725
00:44:48,014 --> 00:44:49,114
<font color="yellow">Was that rude?</font>

726
00:44:49,644 --> 00:44:50,714
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

727
00:44:51,014 --> 00:44:53,544
<font color="yellow">I'm working at contents marketing team.</font>

728
00:44:55,144 --> 00:44:56,274
<font color="yellow">That sounds like a fancy job.</font>

729
00:44:57,674 --> 00:45:00,374
<font color="yellow">It may sound like it, but that's not really true.</font>

730
00:45:01,944 --> 00:45:04,514
<font color="yellow">But your father is so proud of you.</font>

731
00:45:05,944 --> 00:45:09,214
<font color="yellow">My father is proud of all of his kids.</font>

732
00:45:10,944 --> 00:45:14,274
<font color="yellow">But he seemed to have even more affection toward you.</font>

733
00:45:15,044 --> 00:45:16,474
<font color="yellow">It's because I'm the youngest.</font>

734
00:45:17,374 --> 00:45:19,274
<font color="yellow">Parents love their youngest kid the most.</font>

735
00:45:26,844 --> 00:45:28,874
<font color="yellow">- Your name is Seong Joon, right? - Right.</font>

736
00:45:30,614 --> 00:45:32,574
<font color="yellow">You're very different from your brothers.</font>

737
00:45:32,944 --> 00:45:34,544
<font color="yellow">You have a different personality.</font>

738
00:45:35,814 --> 00:45:37,144
<font color="yellow">You are very good looking as well.</font>

739
00:45:38,314 --> 00:45:39,914
<font color="yellow">No, that's not true.</font>

740
00:45:40,344 --> 00:45:42,114
<font color="yellow">My brothers are better than me.</font>

741
00:45:43,974 --> 00:45:44,974
<font color="yellow">Right.</font>

742
00:45:45,414 --> 00:45:48,274
<font color="yellow">Thank you for taking Seong Sik home...</font>

743
00:45:48,544 --> 00:45:49,874
<font color="yellow">the other day.</font>

744
00:45:50,574 --> 00:45:53,044
<font color="yellow">I should have thanked you earlier.</font>

745
00:45:53,714 --> 00:45:57,644
<font color="yellow">You're welcome. I just ran into him that day.</font>

746
00:45:58,544 --> 00:46:01,274
<font color="yellow">Usually, he's not like that at all.</font>

747
00:46:02,344 --> 00:46:04,944
<font color="yellow">I think he had some problem that day.</font>

748
00:46:06,414 --> 00:46:09,074
<font color="yellow">I understand. Don't worry.</font>

749
00:46:09,814 --> 00:46:12,514
<font color="yellow">Anyway, Seong Joon and my family...</font>

750
00:46:12,714 --> 00:46:15,074
<font color="yellow">owe you a lot.</font>

751
00:46:15,914 --> 00:46:18,514
<font color="yellow">Please let me treat you to a good meal someday.</font>

752
00:46:21,344 --> 00:46:23,944
<font color="yellow">Do you like drinking?</font>

753
00:46:24,244 --> 00:46:26,874
<font color="yellow">Yes, as much as others do.</font>

754
00:46:28,344 --> 00:46:30,774
<font color="yellow">Then, let's have drinks later.</font>

755
00:46:31,514 --> 00:46:32,674
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

756
00:46:34,374 --> 00:46:36,814
<font color="yellow">Good night, then.</font>

757
00:46:37,014 --> 00:46:38,414
<font color="yellow">It was nice to meet you.</font>

758
00:46:42,044 --> 00:46:43,074
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

759
00:46:48,974 --> 00:46:51,544
<font color="yellow">By the way, Jeong Eun is...</font>

760
00:46:53,074 --> 00:46:54,914
<font color="yellow">a soft touch.</font>

761
00:46:55,744 --> 00:46:56,844
<font color="yellow">Please be nice to her.</font>

762
00:47:10,874 --> 00:47:13,274
<font color="yellow">I was fired right away and didn't get any pay.</font>

763
00:47:13,514 --> 00:47:15,574
<font color="yellow">I should have written the scenario instead.</font>

764
00:47:16,844 --> 00:47:19,574
<font color="yellow">How can they steal my project proposal?</font>

765
00:47:20,274 --> 00:47:22,674
<font color="yellow">I won't just sit back. Tomorrow...</font>

766
00:47:22,844 --> 00:47:24,544
<font color="yellow">Should I write about it online?</font>

767
00:47:25,414 --> 00:47:27,474
<font color="yellow">Why don't you take some rest?</font>

768
00:47:27,474 --> 00:47:29,944
<font color="yellow">Why are you standing and murmuring in the middle of the room?</font>

769
00:47:30,144 --> 00:47:32,244
<font color="yellow">- It's nothing. - Did you have dinner?</font>

770
00:47:32,814 --> 00:47:34,174
<font color="yellow">No, I didn't and I won't.</font>

771
00:47:36,044 --> 00:47:37,074
<font color="yellow">Why not?</font>

772
00:47:37,974 --> 00:47:40,574
<font color="yellow">I'm busy. I will rather write the scenario.</font>

773
00:47:41,574 --> 00:47:45,474
<font color="yellow">Are you not studying with Seong Joon today?</font>

774
00:47:46,614 --> 00:47:48,614
<font color="yellow">We don't study together every day.</font>

775
00:47:48,874 --> 00:47:50,714
<font color="yellow">Writing isn't a team work.</font>

776
00:47:51,444 --> 00:47:52,644
<font color="yellow">By the way,</font>

777
00:47:53,874 --> 00:47:57,474
<font color="yellow">you work for the same company as Seong Joon, right?</font>

778
00:47:59,844 --> 00:48:01,514
<font color="yellow">How did you know that?</font>

779
00:48:01,614 --> 00:48:04,814
<font color="yellow">Of course, Ms. Hwang told me.</font>

780
00:48:06,214 --> 00:48:10,014
<font color="yellow">I heard that he brought his fiance home the other day.</font>

781
00:48:11,744 --> 00:48:12,774
<font color="yellow">He did.</font>

782
00:48:12,874 --> 00:48:15,944
<font color="yellow">You should have told me about it earlier.</font>

783
00:48:15,944 --> 00:48:17,474
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you tell me?</font>

784
00:48:18,344 --> 00:48:21,714
<font color="yellow">He's your boss after all.</font>

785
00:48:21,844 --> 00:48:25,114
<font color="yellow">I should thank him for helping you.</font>

786
00:48:25,144 --> 00:48:26,514
<font color="yellow">This isn't right.</font>

787
00:48:27,014 --> 00:48:30,514
<font color="yellow">I didn't tell you because I didn't want to make you feel uncomfortable.</font>

788
00:48:31,014 --> 00:48:34,014
<font color="yellow">Still, I should thank him, anyway.</font>

789
00:48:34,974 --> 00:48:36,144
<font color="yellow">I am sorry.</font>

790
00:48:39,814 --> 00:48:40,814
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui,</font>

791
00:48:42,174 --> 00:48:45,374
<font color="yellow">you can write more comfortably without me, right?</font>

792
00:48:45,574 --> 00:48:48,314
<font color="yellow">No, Grandma. You can stay here.</font>

793
00:48:48,474 --> 00:48:51,544
<font color="yellow">I'll just sleep downstairs.</font>

794
00:48:52,214 --> 00:48:55,944
<font color="yellow">Write as much as you want.</font>

795
00:48:56,844 --> 00:48:59,974
<font color="yellow">Why does she want me to sleep over these days?</font>

796
00:49:12,474 --> 00:49:13,644
<font color="yellow">Who is it?</font>

797
00:49:17,544 --> 00:49:18,574
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

798
00:49:19,674 --> 00:49:22,074
<font color="yellow">I was waiting for you.</font>

799
00:49:22,314 --> 00:49:26,114
<font color="yellow">Will you make a scene again tonight?</font>

800
00:49:27,174 --> 00:49:28,344
<font color="yellow">I won't.</font>

801
00:49:29,374 --> 00:49:31,674
<font color="yellow">I heard about everything.</font>

802
00:49:36,114 --> 00:49:39,814
<font color="yellow">I will thank you later. Have a good time.</font>

803
00:49:41,244 --> 00:49:43,774
<font color="yellow">- See you tomorrow. - Good night.</font>

804
00:49:53,874 --> 00:49:56,744
<font color="yellow">What made you so scary that you want to sleep with me?</font>

805
00:49:56,914 --> 00:50:00,344
<font color="yellow">I think I'm too stressed because of my grandchildren.</font>

806
00:50:00,814 --> 00:50:02,644
<font color="yellow">I fell asleep,</font>

807
00:50:03,274 --> 00:50:05,644
<font color="yellow">and the grim reaper was...</font>

808
00:50:06,074 --> 00:50:08,944
<font color="yellow">sitting right there.</font>

809
00:50:09,074 --> 00:50:11,044
<font color="yellow">It was really scary. Goodness.</font>

810
00:50:11,214 --> 00:50:12,714
<font color="yellow">Then,</font>

811
00:50:13,114 --> 00:50:16,444
<font color="yellow">you should have just followed him.</font>

812
00:50:16,514 --> 00:50:18,574
<font color="yellow">Why did you send him away empty-handed?</font>

813
00:50:18,674 --> 00:50:20,774
<font color="yellow">How can you say that?</font>

814
00:50:20,774 --> 00:50:24,574
<font color="yellow">Are you saying I should have died last night?</font>

815
00:50:24,714 --> 00:50:27,974
<font color="yellow">Let's not be petty.</font>

816
00:50:28,714 --> 00:50:32,044
<font color="yellow">We live with a lot of risks every day.</font>

817
00:50:32,314 --> 00:50:34,674
<font color="yellow">- The grim reaper is nothing. - What?</font>

818
00:50:35,344 --> 00:50:37,674
<font color="yellow">- What risks are you talking about? - Forget it.</font>

819
00:50:37,914 --> 00:50:39,074
<font color="yellow">Let's go to bed.</font>

820
00:50:39,274 --> 00:50:42,974
<font color="yellow">Fine, I am petty. I want to live longer. Is that wrong?</font>

821
00:50:43,314 --> 00:50:44,944
<font color="yellow">You're unbelievable.</font>

822
00:50:49,374 --> 00:50:51,874
<font color="yellow">You called me over for nothing.</font>

823
00:50:52,144 --> 00:50:53,514
<font color="yellow">You can't say it's nothing.</font>

824
00:50:53,974 --> 00:50:56,374
<font color="yellow">Aren't you afraid of death?</font>

825
00:50:58,114 --> 00:51:01,744
<font color="yellow">I'd rather die than keep living like this.</font>

826
00:51:01,944 --> 00:51:05,214
<font color="yellow">- What? - Look at me.</font>

827
00:51:06,144 --> 00:51:09,214
<font color="yellow">I still have to work hard at this age.</font>

828
00:51:09,214 --> 00:51:10,544
<font color="yellow">I don't have my own house,</font>

829
00:51:10,814 --> 00:51:14,174
<font color="yellow">so I'm living in my in-law's house with my granddaughter.</font>

830
00:51:14,474 --> 00:51:17,814
<font color="yellow">It's such a harsh life, so I'd rather be dead.</font>

831
00:51:18,114 --> 00:51:19,214
<font color="yellow">By the way,</font>

832
00:51:20,374 --> 00:51:22,244
<font color="yellow">I heard that Dong Hui is a writer.</font>

833
00:51:23,174 --> 00:51:26,644
<font color="yellow">She does. Seong Joon is with her.</font>

834
00:51:27,444 --> 00:51:30,574
<font color="yellow">I think they'll have a discussion over night.</font>

835
00:51:31,144 --> 00:51:32,944
<font color="yellow">Speaking of it,</font>

836
00:51:32,974 --> 00:51:35,514
<font color="yellow">why don't you live on this floor?</font>

837
00:51:36,244 --> 00:51:37,244
<font color="yellow">Pardon?</font>

838
00:51:37,244 --> 00:51:40,374
<font color="yellow">Writing requires a great deal of concentration...</font>

839
00:51:40,374 --> 00:51:42,674
<font color="yellow">and sensitivity.</font>

840
00:51:42,774 --> 00:51:46,144
<font color="yellow">If you stay with her and snore while she writes,</font>

