<font color="yellow">Really? My script is a runner-up in the short drama section?</font>

1053
01:04:37,144 --> 01:04:38,174
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

1054
01:04:38,344 --> 01:04:40,244
<font color="yellow">Please bring your identification card and your stamp...</font>

1055
01:04:40,274 --> 01:04:41,444
<font color="yellow">to the headquarter.</font>

1056
01:04:42,674 --> 01:04:43,914
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

1057
01:05:01,044 --> 01:05:02,114
<font color="yellow">Excuse me.</font>

1058
01:05:11,344 --> 01:05:12,444
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

1059
01:05:14,044 --> 01:05:15,044
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui.</font>

1060
01:05:19,214 --> 01:05:21,744
<font color="yellow">Something great happen to me.</font>

1061
01:05:21,814 --> 01:05:23,644
<font color="yellow">I wanted to let you know first.</font>

1062
01:05:27,144 --> 01:05:28,514
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon!</font>

1063
01:05:39,114 --> 01:05:40,744
<font color="yellow">How could you do this?</font>

1064
01:05:47,274 --> 01:05:48,314
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui.</font>

1065
01:05:49,714 --> 01:05:51,114
<font color="yellow">I quit my job today.</font>

1066
01:05:53,044 --> 01:05:55,914
<font color="yellow">I hope you'll do great even if I'm not here.</font>

1067
01:05:56,674 --> 01:05:57,674
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

1068
01:06:00,274 --> 01:06:01,314
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

1069
01:06:24,174 --> 01:06:25,314
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

1070
01:06:31,644 --> 01:06:32,674
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

1071
01:06:33,744 --> 01:06:35,574
<font color="yellow">- What? - Are you going out?</font>

1072
01:06:36,714 --> 01:06:38,644
<font color="yellow">- Yes. - Where?</font>

1073
01:06:39,574 --> 01:06:41,244
<font color="yellow">I'm not sure.</font>

1074
01:06:41,874 --> 01:06:42,914
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

1075
01:06:44,914 --> 01:06:46,414
<font color="yellow">Sit down for a minute.</font>

1076
01:06:47,944 --> 01:06:48,974
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

1077
01:06:51,714 --> 01:06:54,374
<font color="yellow">- On the day we had rice cake soup, - Yes.</font>

1078
01:06:55,114 --> 01:06:57,544
<font color="yellow">A guy named Mr. Lee came over.</font>

1079
01:06:58,844 --> 01:07:00,274
<font color="yellow">You like him, don't you?</font>

1080
01:07:02,814 --> 01:07:05,174
<font color="yellow">My gosh. I knew it.</font>

1081
01:07:06,074 --> 01:07:07,644
<font color="yellow">This is driving me crazy.</font>

1082
01:07:08,114 --> 01:07:09,514
<font color="yellow">How did you know?</font>

1083
01:07:09,944 --> 01:07:11,944
<font color="yellow">It's all written on your face.</font>

1084
01:07:13,944 --> 01:07:15,944
<font color="yellow">Grandma and the rest of the family don't know.</font>

1085
01:07:16,044 --> 01:07:18,344
<font color="yellow">They're all blind fools who can't see anything.</font>

1086
01:07:22,014 --> 01:07:23,374
<font color="yellow">Listen to me carefully.</font>

1087
01:07:24,144 --> 01:07:26,174
<font color="yellow">- I can't let you see him. - What?</font>

1088
01:07:26,414 --> 01:07:27,574
<font color="yellow">Why not?</font>

1089
01:07:51,774 --> 01:07:52,844
<font color="yellow">- What are you doing? - Gosh.</font>

1090
01:07:55,214 --> 01:07:57,244
<font color="yellow">- I'm going out on a date. - Pardon?</font>

1091
01:07:58,114 --> 01:08:00,214
<font color="yellow">You told me to give her what she wants.</font>

1092
01:08:20,114 --> 01:08:21,884
<font color="yellow">(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

1093
01:08:22,444 --> 01:08:24,544
<font color="yellow">So where is my brother, Sang Woo?</font>

1094
01:08:24,614 --> 01:08:27,614
<font color="yellow">He'd be around the same age as my cousin, Seong Joon.</font>

1095
01:08:28,074 --> 01:08:29,444
<font color="yellow">I've wished...</font>

1096
01:08:29,544 --> 01:08:32,314
<font color="yellow">you'd stay well and healthy all my life.</font>

1097
01:08:32,444 --> 01:08:34,344
<font color="yellow">- Eat this. - My dear Ah In.</font>

1098
01:08:34,414 --> 01:08:37,714
<font color="yellow">How would you feel if you have to live with me?</font>

1099
01:08:37,744 --> 01:08:39,444
<font color="yellow">Please forgive me.</font>

1100
01:08:40,414 --> 01:08:41,544
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

1101
01:08:41,544 --> 01:08:44,884
<font color="yellow">Are we going to sleep here together tonight?</font>

1102
01:08:44,974 --> 01:08:46,884
<font color="yellow">This is all for Seong Joon's sake.</font>

1103
01:08:47,114 --> 01:08:49,114
<font color="yellow">I'm just an office assistant. Even if I talk to him,</font>

1104
01:08:49,674 --> 01:08:51,144
<font color="yellow">it wouldn't make any difference.</font>

